<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">The holiday season is a time of giving, and at Teamwork Commerce, we believe in supporting the communities we call home. This year, our teams around the world came together to make a difference in the lives of others.</p>

<h2>Mexico team</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">In Querétaro, the Mexico team prepared and delivered 100 Christmas meals to two local hospitals, bringing warmth and nourishment to those in need during the festive season.</p>

<h2>London team</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">In the UK, the London team donated essential food items to the Euston Food Bank, helping families facing food insecurity find some relief during the holidays.</p>

<h2>Clearwater team</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">In the U.S., the Clearwater team joined forces with Toys for Tots, donating toys and volunteering their time to ensure children in the community experience the magic of the season.</p>

<h2>A shared commitment</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">At Teamwork Commerce, we recognize how fortunate we are and are committed to giving back. These initiatives are just one way we show gratitude and spread joy during the holidays. Together, we can make a meaningful impact, one act of kindness at a time.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Happy Holidays from all of us at Teamwork Commerce.</p>
